query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 t1 tq1 s) NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('cron',
'floor-function',
'hyperbolic-geometry',
'icons',
'power-management',
'software-recommendation',
'transformation',
'weak-convergence',
'windows-10',
'windows-7')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 100
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Citizen Patrol',
'Cleanup',
'Disciplined',
'Enthusiast',
'Investor',
'Nice Answer',
'Peer Pressure',
'Promoter') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
